These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, prince, havana, game
1. the fonseca-smoker is somewhere to the right of the game-smoker##5
2. the fonseca-smoker is somewhere to the left of the havana-smoker##5
3. the fonseca-smoker is between the game-smoker and the prince-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2     |     3      |  4   |
| Cigar   | game | fonseca | prince | havana |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, animation, sports, martial-arts
1. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching action movies##5
3. the person watching sports movies is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |       4       |
| Movie-Genre   | action | martial-arts | animation | sports |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, fanta, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person drinking coffee is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person drinking iced-tea is the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | iced-tea | fanta | coffee |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, ice-hockey, rugby, cycling
1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |   4    |
| Sport   | cycling | ice-hockey | rugby | swimming |

