.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-5::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, orange, peach, broccoli
1. the person eating orange is between the person eating broccoli and the person eating peach##2
2. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person eating apple##1
3. the person eating broccoli is somewhere to the right of the person eating peach##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Food   | peach | orange | broccoli | apple |

