.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-6::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, red, mauve, light-blue
1. the person who likes red is in an even position##4
2. the person who likes light-blue is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who likes red##1
4. the person who likes mauve is somewhere to the right of the person who likes brown##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |   3    |    4    |
| Color   | brown | red | mauve | light-blue |

