.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, fishing, sudoku, hiking
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |  3   |   4    |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | hiking | fishing | sudoku |

