.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-9::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, march, may, july
1. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
2. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5
3. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |      2       |     3     |    4    |
| Birthday   | september | march | july | may |

